{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_2__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 2, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "word_start": 0, "word_end": 17, "word_count": 17, "language_hint": "en", "text": "This generic 12 step approach is applicable to all organisations, regardless of their size, type or industry."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_3__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 3, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "word_start": 0, "word_end": 20, "word_count": 20, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Secure the backing you need to successfully implement ISO 27001 by gaining the endorsement and commitment of your organization's leadership"}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_4__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 4, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "word_start": 0, "word_end": 24, "word_count": 24, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Define the boundaries of your ISO 27001 implementation by identifying the parts of your organization, the information, and the systems that will be included."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_5__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 5, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "word_start": 0, "word_end": 13, "word_count": 13, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Identify gaps between the current and the desired state of your security programme."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_6__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 6, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "word_start": 0, "word_end": 22, "word_count": 22, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Establish a strong foundation for your information security management system by creating a policy that outlines your organization's security objectives and commitments."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_7__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 7, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "word_start": 0, "word_end": 22, "word_count": 22, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Enhance your information security by assessing, developing, and documenting the competence of personnel, ensuring they meet the necessary security standards and objectives."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_8__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 8, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "word_start": 0, "word_end": 24, "word_count": 24, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Get a clear view of what needs to be protected by cataloging all the information assets within the scope of your ISO 27001 implementation."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_9__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 9, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "word_start": 0, "word_end": 24, "word_count": 24, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Choose a risk management methodology that fits your organization, ensuring you can effectively identify and evaluate the security risks that threaten your information assets."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_10__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 10, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "word_start": 0, "word_end": 19, "word_count": 19, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Gain insight into the potential threats and vulnerabilities facing your information assets, and assess their potential impact and likelihood."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_11__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 11, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "word_start": 0, "word_end": 26, "word_count": 26, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Decide on the best approach to manage each identified risk, whether it's reducing, retaining, transferring, or avoiding it, and then put the appropriate controls in place."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_12__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 12, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "word_start": 0, "word_end": 21, "word_count": 21, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Continuously monitor and measure your information security management system's performance to ensure it's effectively managing risks and achieving your security objectives."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_13__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 13, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "word_start": 0, "word_end": 17, "word_count": 17, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Keep your information security management system up-to-date and resilient by continually identifying and implementing opportunities for improvement."}
{"chunk_id": "iso6__page_14__chunk_0001", "document_id": "iso6", "source_document_id": "iso6", "framework": "iso27001", "country": "", "source_type": "standard_supporting_text", "is_official": "false", "relative_path": "ISO27001\\iso6.pdf", "unit_type": "page", "unit_number": 14, "chunk_index_in_unit": 1, "word_start": 0, "word_end": 22, "word_count": 22, "language_hint": "en", "text": "Validate your efforts and demonstrate your organization's commitment to information security by successfully undergoing an external audit to achieve ISO 27001 certification."}
